   Directions to the Baltimore VA Medical Center

   To reach the Baltimore VA Medical Center, you need to remember only a
   few simple directions. From Interstate 95, take the exit for Interstate
   395 to Downtown Baltimore and exit onto Martin Luther King, Jr.
   Boulevard. At the fourth traffic light, turn right onto Baltimore
   Street. Take Baltimore Street to the second traffic light and turn left
   onto Paca Street. Take Paca Street to the first traffic light and turn
   left onto Fayette Street. Take Facet Street through the first traffic
   light and the entrance to the medical center's parking garage is a
   half-block down on the left on Fayette past the intersection with
   Greene Street.

Medical Center Address:


    VA Maryland Health Care System
    Baltimore Medical Center
    10 North Greene Street
    Baltimore, Maryland 21201



Medical Center Phone Number

   The phone number for the Baltimore VA Medical Center is (410) 605-7000
   and the toll free number is 1-800-463-6295.

